* RHEL 6 may not shutdown vm automatically after install , it need be shutdown 
  manually to continue the playbook.

* RHEL 6 may not properly configure the network when using static ip address, 
  you should press "Enter" several times to acqire the kitchstart file.

* SELinux is disabled in ks, if enabled, ssh publickey login may fail due to 
  SELinux context problem.
